::Feline::

She timidly looked up at Prowl and didn't look away this time.
She had fear in her eyes. "I..ah..." She glanced at Arcangle.  She 
looked down again. "nothing."
She looked at Iron Raptor. "May I go and get some water from the mess 
hall.  I need to go walk for a bit. Please." She showed her 
uneasiness about being in the room with two males she didn't know.
